parameters.name: START TIME
parameters.description:
Spacecraft event time (UT) at which the particle counting begins.       
      Time is given in the format of `yyyy-mm-ddThh:mm:ss.sss'.

parameters.name: R6A_FLUX
parameters.description:
Flux measured in HET energy channel R6A (1.8-3.2 MeV electrons).        
      The coincidence logic for this channel is A1.^A2.B.^C1.

parameters.name: R6B_FLUX
parameters.description:
Flux measured in HET energy channel R6B (3.2-5.1 MeV electrons).        
      The coincidence logic for this channel is A1.^A2.B.C1.^C2.

parameters.name: R7A_FLUX
parameters.description:
Flux measured in HET energy channel R7A (5.1-8.0 MeV electrons).        
      The coincidence logic for this channel is A1.^A2.B.C1.C2.^C3.
